{"tid":1304420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"睇連登多，社會真係一面倒反修倒支持抗爭？","createTime":"2019-07-10T15:10:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T15:25:38.000Z","uid":112551,"like":6,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"80aa53f342228dcd6196fffbf24786acb3a5aa51","tid":1304420,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:10:53.000Z","msg":"因為我都見一啲Post 話家中廢老仲支持政府同警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n我上連登多，Facebook都係Like 立場相近的Page，我啲朋友都係反修例。<br />\n即使民建聯個啲藍屍Page都係由反修例的人割據，藍屍少講野可能自知理虧，但都未必反映到社會真係一面倒反修倒支持抗爭。"},{"pid":"f58e140be8001fa7006ed08b9a9703fcab1308e1","tid":1304420,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:11:39.000Z","msg":"目前戰線太多，運動重心稍為偏離；大家花太多時間係寶礦力同連儂場上面。<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地需要集中火力係五大訴求上面。</span></span></strong>只有個議題仲係度，個運動先繼續有力量做其他野。重心要放返係「送中」上面，連帶反黑警；連儂場唔好太執著、反TVB唔好反多過林鄭。先搞「送中」，燈柱同信用評分先慢慢普及。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">重心一定要放返係「送中」上面！<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聚焦五大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連儂牆由得佢，第日再整過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2387482604810123/posts/2908010702757308?s=625469440&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=xmo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2387482604810123%2Fposts%2F2908010702757308%3Fs%3D625469440%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dxmo&d=RGEj3L6UPYZQbhamDwVV3Qy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=7b15c889\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2387482604810123/posts/2908010702757308?s=625469440&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=xmo</a>"},{"pid":"8da2af6bc8e5ad72cb14f8ecf9699dd33943db56","tid":1304420,"uid":108512,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:11:45.000Z","msg":"啱呀，得200萬人遊行，應該有500萬人支持修例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class